## Included Icon Licenses

This plugin includes icons from two external sources. Their licenses require attribution:

### freeboard-sk Icons (Apache License 2.0)

Some icons are derived from the *freeboard-sk* project, licensed under the Apache License 2.0.


### OpenCPN Standard Icons (GPLv2)

Some icons are based on or derived from OpenCPNâ€™s standard icon set, licensed under GPLv2.


Because GPLv2 is the stricter license, it governs the entire plugin.  
All included assets are compatible with GPLv2.

